body.description: Celebrate the ones you love with this bold all occasion gift bag with tissue paper. Featuring abstract squares of orange, white, black, green and blue, this large gift bag includes a gift tag that reads "Your Day Your Way" and orange ribbon handles. Purchase includes 3 sheets of black tissue paper to make wrapping gifts for birthdays, Father's Day, graduations and more quick and easy. The Hallmark brand is widely recognized as the very best for greeting cards, gift wrap, and more. For more than 100 years, Hallmark has been helping its customers make everyday moments more beautiful and celebrations more joyful.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Life is a Special Occasion Whether it's saying good luck, thank you, or thinking of you, show how much you care with premium gift bags from Hallmark.

Make Every Day a Celebration Surprise Care Packages Show friends and family you're thinking of them with a small gift bag filled with tea, snacks and a thoughtful note. Pro Tip: Gift bags with handles make it easy to hang on door knobs for socially distanced gift giving. Cheerful Gifts of Gratitude Bright and cheery gift bags are perfect for thanking postal workers, caregivers and other essential workers for keeping the world turning. Pro Tip: Buy bag bundles in bulk to have on hand for brightening someone's day in an instant. Cute (and Disposable!) Lunch Bags Make lunchtime more fun by using colorful paper treat sacks instead of a lunchbox. Best of all, disposable lunch bags can help keep germs from coming home. Pro Tip: Add a note of encouragement to make your loved one smile in the middle of their day.
